speech.p:
asked the Minister of Housing and Local Government (1) whether he will renew his pre- 
decessor's undertaking with regard to any jointly agreed scheme which the colleges and City of Oxford might put forward as an alternative basis of assessment of the rate liability of the Oxford colleges;

(2) when he will announce the outcome of his dicussions with the Chancellor of the Exchequer upon the possibility of special grants being made to Oxford and Cambridge colleges through the University Grants Committee in lieu of rates.
